**Example 1: 开启通道**



Input: 

```
tccli gaap OpenProxies --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --ProxyIds link-11113333 link-11112222
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "OperationFailedInstanceSet": [],
        "RequestId": "7daaa62c-7c4b-40d9-a22e-90de42bde58d",
        "InvalidStatusInstanceSet": []
    }
}
```
